/></item><item><title>第14章 Cargo与Crates.io</title><link>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/chapter_14.html</link><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/chapter_14.html</guid><description/></item><item><title>第15章 智能指针 (Smart Pointers)</title><link>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/chapter_15.html</link><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/chapter_15.html</guid><description/></item><item><title>第16章 无畏并发 (Fearless Concurrency)</title><link>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/chapter_16.html</link><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/chapter_16.html</guid><description/></item><item><title>第17章 面向对象编程特性 (OOP)</title><link>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/chapter_17.html</link><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/chapter_17.html</guid><description/></item><item><title>第18章 模式和匹配 (Patterns &amp; Matching)</title><link>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/chapter_18.html</link><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/chapter_18.html</guid><description/></item><item><title>第19章 高级特性 (Advanced Features)</title><link>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/chapter_19.html</link><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/chapter_19.html</guid><description/></item><item><title>第1章 入门指南 (Getting Started)</title><link>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/chapter_1.html</link><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/chapter_1.html</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;本章内容：安装 Rust、编写第一个程序、使用 Cargo 管理项目。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="11-安装"&gt;1.1 安装&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Rust 通过 &lt;code&gt;rustup&lt;/code&gt; 安装，这是 Rust 版本管理和工具链管理器。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="ln"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;curl --proto &lt;span class="s1"&gt;&amp;#39;=https&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; --tlsv1.2 -sSf https://sh.rustup.rs &lt;span class="p"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; sh
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;安装后验证：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="ln"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;rustc --version &lt;span class="c1"&gt;# 输出类似 rustc x.y.z (abcabcabc yyyy-mm-dd)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="ln"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;cargo --version
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;额外依赖&lt;/strong&gt;：Rust 需要一个 C 编译器来链接。Arch 用 &lt;code&gt;pacman -S base-devel&lt;/code&gt;，Ubuntu 用 &lt;code&gt;apt install build-essential&lt;/code&gt;，macOS 用 &lt;code&gt;xcode-select --install&lt;/code&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;常用管理命令：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="ln"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;rustup update &lt;span class="c1"&gt;# 更新 Rust&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="ln"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;rustup self uninstall &lt;span class="c1"&gt;# 卸载&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="ln"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;rustup doc &lt;span class="c1"&gt;# 打开本地离线文档&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;div class="admonition important"&gt;
 &lt;div class="admonition-header"&gt;&lt;svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 512 512"&gt;&lt;path d="M256 512A256 256 0 1 0 256 0a256 256 0 1 0 0 512zm0-384c13.3 0 24 10.7 24 24l0 112c0 13.3-10.7 24-24 24s-24-10.7-24-24l0-112c0-13.3 10.7-24 24-24zM224 352a32 32 0 1 1 64 0 32 32 0 1 1 -64 0z"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;span&gt;稳定性保证&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;div class="admonition-content"&gt;
 &lt;p&gt;Rust 编译器保证向后兼容。本书所有能编译的示例，在新版本中依然能通过编译。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>第20章 最后的项目：多线程Web服务器</title><link>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/chapter_20.html</link><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/chapter_20.html</guid><description/></item><item><title>第2章 猜数字游戏 (Guessing Game)</title><link>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/chapter_2.html</link><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/chapter_2.html</guid><description/></item><item><title>第3章 通用编程概念 (Common Concepts)</title><link>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/chapter_3.html</link><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/chapter_3.html</guid><description/></item><item><title>第4章 认识所有权 (Understanding Ownership)</title><link>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/chapter_4.html</link><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/chapter_4.html</guid><description/></item><item><title>第5章 使用结构体组织相关数据 (Structs)</title><link>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/chapter_5.html</link><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/chapter_5.html</guid><description/></item><item><title>第6章 枚举和模式匹配 (Enums &amp; Patterns)</title><link>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/chapter_6.html</link><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/chapter_6.html</guid><description/></item><item><title>第7章 包/Crate/模块 (Packages, Crates, Modules)</title><link>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/chapter_7.html</link><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/chapter_7.html</guid><description/></item><item><title>第8章 常见集合 (Common Collections)</title><link>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/chapter_8.html</link><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/chapter_8.html</guid><description/></item><item><title>第9章 错误处理 (Error Handling)</title><link>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/chapter_9.html</link><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/chapter_9.html</guid><description/></item><item><title>附录 (Appendix)</title><link>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/appendix.html</link><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hugo-dead-simple.netlify.com/books/rust%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/appendix.html</guid><description/></item></channel></rss>